"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This closure\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 364}, {\"ngram\": \"signs\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 492}, {\"ngram\": \"the rail infrastructure\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 528}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Infrabel has identified aging issues in thehigh-speedline connecting Brussels to the French-Belgian border.\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 638, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 531, \"end\": 539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Infrabel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Infrabel\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Infrabel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Infrabel\"}, {\"begin\": 600, \"end\": 608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brussels-South_railway_station\", \"score\": 0.999999916700748, \"rank\": 8.329873127133798e-08, \"text\": \"Brussels\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brussels-South_railway_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brussels-South_railway_station\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"aging issues\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 567}, {\"ngram\": \"the French-Belgian border\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 637}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This section, the oldest on Belgium's high-speed network, is now 27 years old.\", \"from\": 640, \"to\": 718, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 668, \"end\": 675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1618705042099763e-18, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This section\", \"from\": 640, \"to\": 652}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To tackle these issues, Infrabel has planned a decade-long renewal project.\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 794, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 743, \"end\": 751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Infrabel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Infrabel\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Infrabel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Infrabel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these issues\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 741}, {\"ngram\": \"a decade-long renewal project\", \"from\": 764, \"to\": 793}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While most of the work will be done at night, a two-week full closure of the line each summer will be necessary.\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 908, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 810, \"to\": 818}, {\"ngram\": \"night\", \"from\": 835, \"to\": 840}, {\"ngram\": \"a two-week full closure\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 865}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 877}, {\"ngram\": \"each summer\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 889}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The engineering works will begin on August 12, immediately following the closing ceremony of the ParisOlympics, which will take place on August 11.\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 1057, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The engineering works\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 931}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 952}, {\"ngram\": \"the closing ceremony\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 999}, {\"ngram\": \"the ParisOlympics\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1020}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 1047, \"to\": 1053}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Over 18 days and nights, technical teams will overhaul one of the two tracks on a 17.6 kilometer stretch between the Belgian towns of Leuze-en-Hainaut and Brugelette.\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1176, \"end\": 1183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0399008934632842e-15, \"text\": \"Belgian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resou